{"tid":789485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"gobee-bike結業首宗申索案-毒男苦主獲賠30港元","createTime":"2018-08-22T09:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T13:45:19.000Z","uid":133528,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de4ecd22e71ee5e092a286c5a20d0623fef2c89c","tid":789485,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】民間組織「沙田脈搏」召集人林宇星就上月突然宣布結業的gobee.bike索償未退還的餘額。林指該公司結業後，未能以其應用程式使用單車，入稟小額錢債審裁處，成功向自行車快樂有限公司，即gobee.bike索償餘額30元及30元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n以應用程式出租單車的自行車快樂有限公司於7月10日向傳媒公佈進行清盤，聲稱只退還按金，餘額則鼓勵用家於公司應用程式停用，即7月17日前使用，所有餘額並不會退還。<br />\n<br />\n申索人稱至7月10日開始，多次使用或嘗試解開該公司被鎖上的單車，惜每次掃描單車上的QR Code，電話只顯示「This bike has been reported as broken」，使申索人無法在限期前使用餘下的充值額，入稟小額錢債審裁處向自行車快樂有限公司索償Gobee.Bike 應用程式內的充值額共30元。<br />\n<br />\n就Gobee.Bike只准許用戶於7月10日至7月17日期間使用餘下的充值額，申索人稱街上單車數目少之又少，而且該公司並無保障所有單車在沒有壞情況下給用家使用，林認為自行車快樂有限公司沒有履行服務承諾。<br />\n<br />\n申索人在庭外訪問稱自己以個別個案申索，但仍有約100名苦主帳戶內尚有餘額，又指Gobee.Bike以共享經濟作名目，集資後潛逃，實在不理想，考慮本港仍有相似單車租借服務，擔心用戶難以受到保障。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/173002_7249950f6c139bd30e234254ce2b7daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F173002_7249950f6c139bd30e234254ce2b7daf.jpg&h=4b810f77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fb933623a780a9fc6988f9854368d11ef0e8407","tid":789485,"uid":101917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"快樂有限公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52470681e9beddaef681939c640045adbe6bbc42","tid":789485,"uid":133528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8fb933623a780a9fc6988f9854368d11ef0e8407","tid":789485,"uid":101917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"快樂有限公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:31:56.000Z","msg":"自行車快樂有限公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbed78c00c0590f2391949977c65bca11c3272c","tid":789485,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10011dc3a15abff06c38fb3b3fcdabd2ba539b06","tid":789485,"uid":192517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"為左正義<br />\n30蚊都要追<br />\n唔係少唔少錢既問題"},{"pid":"d3c8cf93d7ecd7c28039b00a4855d657c7a0e942","tid":789485,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10011dc3a15abff06c38fb3b3fcdabd2ba539b06","tid":789485,"uid":192517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"為左正義<br />\n30蚊都要追<br />\n唔係少唔少錢既問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:59:21.000Z","msg":"車費唔計?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf055d1a4db7658cd1412916ca4b3279eb29a2c","tid":789485,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"邊位青"},{"pid":"ee58313b86ed3154e065a026d94b7de1d269d03b","tid":789485,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"中學師弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bbdaa6049acb17ac50ed17c3df0b2c9f04772b","tid":789485,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"Btw又唔好個個都話人毒男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715020d7a161daeddf2a3f5657ac66c96c273444","tid":789485,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"法律根本應該係咁用, 但香港得小額錢債可以咁玩<br />\n多過5皮野要請律師互片, 但又唔可以包攬訴訟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3470a587f9547183c862ecb899b09e51b9655071","tid":789485,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:45:19.000Z